title: Cuisinart PowerPrep Plus Food Processor
description: Cooking and clean up is a snap with the next generation of the Cuisinart food processor.

asset.author: CuisinartVideo
asset.hookText: Cooking and clean up is a snap with the next generation of the Cuisinart food processor. See more at http://www.cuisinart.com/catalog/product.php?product_id=298&item_id=400&cat_id=7

transcripts: Cuisinart the next generation. New lines, new engineering, new capabilities. Introducing the powerprep plus food processor from Cuisinart. From bread dough to pizza to stir fry. From salsa  to apple pie we do the work to save you time. Even clean up is a snap. Makes everyday meals easy and guest welcome any time. Experience the next generation of the Cuisinart food processor and savor the good life. The powerprep plus available at fine stores everywhere.
